{"tid":727983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[上帝再臨]平老馬助攻紀錄 美斯淘汰賽踢出逆天表現","createTime":"2018-07-03T12:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T13:33:05.000Z","uid":163207,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"030f281ac3270994a256eeb7c2f606d2c117fecd","tid":727983,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:24:34.000Z","msg":"阿根廷出局，美斯卻追平了馬勒當拿的紀錄，成為自1986世盃後另一位單場再獻兩記助攻的阿根廷球員。<br />\n<br />\n美斯今仗於下半場早段的轉身射門，省中加比爾馬卡度改變方向入網變助攻，至補時階段再送過頭波給阿古路頂成3:4，貢獻了兩記助攻，成為馬勒當拿在86世盃分組賽首戰對南韓後，新一位在世盃單場助攻「起孖」的阿根廷球員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e2b739994d287cd1339cd11762934661b80948","tid":727983,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94deb16d24a8e050296f8af608a1e7740dd9cfe4","tid":727983,"uid":84834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"5.55球王又破紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9deb073850ad8d9f3e9f79096542d8bb7fccf5","tid":727983,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94deb16d24a8e050296f8af608a1e7740dd9cfe4","tid":727983,"uid":84834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"5.55球王又破紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"講緊32年以嚟第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}